http://www.conservative.org:80/discovery/perot.html 204.71.237.88 19970209001749 text/html 7552
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 00:18:22 GMT
Last-modified: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 08:34:14 GMT
