<P></center>
<blockquote>
<b><i>"The seat at the table that once belonged to radical environmentalists now belongs to Senator Wallop and the Frontiers of Freedom Institute."</b></i><br>
<ul><ul>U.S. Senator Lauch Faircloth (R-NC)<br> Chairman, Senate subcommittee on clean air, wetlands, private property and nuclear safety
</ul></ul>
</blockquote><p>
